==English==
===Etymology===
Representing "internationalization" as "i" followed by 18 more letters, followed by "n".

===Noun===
'''i18n'''
#{{softeng}} [[Internationalization]].

====Alternative forms====
*'''I18N'''
*'''I18n'''

====Usage notes====
*The preferred spelling is '''i18n''', as the upper-case ''I'' ("eye") is indistinguishable from a lower-case ''l'' ("el") in many [[sans serif]] [[font]]s.

